run_count = 0
jobs_found = False
for next_schedule, function_object in doccron.run_jobs(simulate=True):
    jobs_found = True
    assert isinstance(next_schedule, datetime)
    assert function_object.__name__ in ('foo', 'bar')
    assert function_object.__name__ != 'baz'
    run_count += 1
    if run_count == 5:
        break
assert jobs_found
